snippet.title: E-Men Anime Intro - Season 57: Hostile Takeover
snippet.description:
http://www.edencorp.tokyo/

It’s official! You asked for it, and now you're getting it -- E-MEN IS BACK!!
 
The number-one anime series is back for a record breaking 57th season in a row! 
 
This time, the evil forces of SYNDIK8 rise up from a radicalized public to lash out at a society they are too entitled to understand! It's sure to be one of our most thrilling arcs yet - and this time it's ripped straight from the headlines!
 
Get ready for 25 all new action packed episodes, premiering this Saturday on Eden Action and available online at Eden’s Show Hub. Don’t miss a second - this season is going to be the best one yet!!
